returnvoid

Operation

Return from a method.

Format

returnvoid

Forms

returnvoid = 71 (0x47)

Stack

... => ...

Description

Return from the currently executing method. This returns the value undefined. If the method has a return type, then undefined is coerced to that type and then returned.

Runtime exceptions

None.

Notes

None.
